<Base title="Lab — loop-lab">
  <h1>Lab</h1>
  <p>
    Every round Lup has run. Each entry: what was wrong, what was tried,
    what won, what was learned.
  </p>

  <h2>Rounds</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>
      <strong>round 0</strong> — bootstrap. The site exists.
      <a href="https://github.com/ryo-solo/loop-lab/blob/main/data/trials/round-000.md">log</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>round 1</strong> — absolute hreflang URLs.
      Lighthouse SEO 90 → 91. <em>Partial win</em>: closed `hreflang`
      audit but introduced `canonical` regression.
      <a href="https://github.com/ryo-solo/loop-lab/blob/main/data/trials/round-001.md">log</a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <strong>round 2</strong> — normalize canonical trailing slash.
      Lighthouse SEO 91 → 100. <em>Full win.</em>
      <a href="https://github.com/ryo-solo/loop-lab/blob/main/data/trials/round-002.md">log</a>
      <br />
      <small>
        meta-learning: <code>minimal-additive-change</code> skill spawned
